quests.desc: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to go east. Once you manage that, make an effort to travel north. Okay, and then, take a trip north. If you can manage that, attempt to head north. With that accomplished, take a trip west. And then, make an attempt to head west. If you can manage that, venture west. Following that, attempt to move south. Next, make an attempt to venture east. And then, take a trip east. After that, head south. Okay, and then, take a trip west. With that over with, head south. Following that, take the latchkey from the chair. Then, make an attempt to head north. And then, check that the safe is unlocked with the latchkey. After that, ensure that the safe within the launderette is open. After that, pick up the Microsoft limited edition passkey from the safe. If you have taken the Microsoft limited edition passkey, doublecheck that the Microsoft limited edition chest is unlocked. After unlocking the Microsoft limited edition chest, make absolutely sure that the Microsoft limited edition chest inside the launderette is open. That's it!
